the following is the text of king 
fahds television address as translated by the the associated press 
</TEXT>
<TEXT>
in the name of god the beneficent the merciful 
brother citizens gods peace mercy and blessings be upon you 
no doubt you know by following the sudden and regrettable 
events in the arabian gulf region during the past few days the 
extent of the dangerous situation confronted by the arab nation 
under the present circumstances 
no doubt you know that the kingdom of saudi arabia has exerted 
all it could in efforts and attempts with each of the governments 
of the republic of iraq and the state of kuwait to contain the 
dispute that developed between the two countries and i undertook 
in this connection a number of telephone contacts and brotherly 
talks as a result a bilateral meeting of iraqi and kuwaiti 
delegations was hosted by the kingdom in the attempts to heal the 
rift and prevent an escalation of matters 
some of the brothers kings and heads of state of the arab 
states contributed vastly and commendably to this end impelled by 
faith in the unity of the arab nation and bolster its march toward 
solidarity and cooperation in a way that achieves complete success 
in these matters of destiny 
but most regrettably matters took a course contrary to what 
we the islamic and arab nations and the entire peaceloving world 
