decisions and favors un solutions to resolve such conflicts 
the resolution says annexation of kuwait by iraq under any 
form and whatever pretext has no legal validity and is considered 
null and void 
it calls upon all states and international organizations not to 
recognize the annexation and not to take any action that might be 
interpreted as inderect recognition of the annexation 
