assembly plant that built the dodge omni and plymouth horizion last 
february 
the spiritacclaim successor will be introduced sometime around 
1995 gardner said those cars were introduced in the spring of 
1989 and are assembled in newark del 
also at the conference ford motor co officially unveiled its 
46liter v8 engine for the 1991 lincoln town car which goes into 
production later this year 
the engine to be built at fords 780 million revamped engine 
plant in romeo mich is the first of the companys modular 
family of engines modular engines give manufacturers flexibility 
and cost reductions by creating common basic engine structure with 
interchangeable components giving each kind of engine its own 
characteristics 
overall we estimate the new family of engines will share 
about 350 parts or about 75 percent of the engine said david f 
hagen general manager of fords engine division new v8 
variations will cost about 60 million to develop compared to about 
500 million for a typical new engine program 
he said the modular engine concept will be expanded to fords 
huge cleveland engine plant which will build a new series of v6 
engines to enter production in the mid1990s 
meantime richard donnelly head of general motors corps newly 
created engine division said the company is moving to consolidate 
its engine research development and manufacturing which could 
close an engine plant sometime in the future 
he did not say which factory may be affected 
