analytical firm said soybeans would draw further support from the 
usdas projected drop in us soybean stockpile 
the government said soybean stocks are likely to fall from an 
estimated 275 million bushels at the end of this month to 225 
million bushels by aug 31 1991 the end of the 199091 crop year 
the latter estimate was 40 million bushels below the usdas july 
projection 
